OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1777381871
OL,3,CBest foot forward: Walking Festival
OL,4,Cgets underway
OL,6,FThe Galashiels Walking Festival has
OL,7,Fkicked off this weekend, in its 10th
OL,8,Fanniversary year.
OL,10,FThere are 16 guided walks taking place
OL,11,Feither leaving from or ending in the
OL,12,FScottish Borders town.
OL,14,FA team of 10 volunteers are credited
OL,15,Ffor making the event such a success by
OL,16,Forganisers Angela Crow and George
OL,17,FCrow, from the Hike and Bike Hub in
OL,18,FGalashiels.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
