OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1777381871
OL,3,CBest foot forward: Walking Festival
OL,4,Cgets underway
OL,6,FAngela Crow said: "People can expect
OL,7,Fto get a little bit of local
OL,8,Finformation about the walk that
OL,9,Fthey're going on because all of the
OL,10,Fwalk leaders will have checked out the
OL,11,Froute they're going to be taking that
OL,12,Fday.
OL,14,F"They will also have lots of stories
OL,15,Ffrom their own experiences to share
OL,16,Fwith the group of walkers on the day."
OL,18,FGeorge Crow said: "We do get people
OL,19,Fcoming back year after year, which is
OL,20,Freally quite surprising for us.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
