PN,35703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1777381871
OL,3,CBest foot forward: Walking Festival
OL,4,Cgets underway
OL,6,F"We didn't expect that when we first
OL,7,Fstarted doing this. And the feedback
OL,8,Fwe get is that people enjoy the
OL,9,Fconversations, they enjoy meeting old
OL,10,Ffriends - because they become old
OL,11,Ffriends.
OL,13,F"Even if it's a walk they've done
OL,14,Fbefore they like coming along and
OL,15,Fgetting a bit of chat and that little
OL,16,Fbit of personal interaction again."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
