CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1777381871
OL,3,CBest foot forward: Walking Festival
OL,4,Cgets underway
OL,6,FOrganisers make sure there are a
OL,7,Fvariety of routes on offer, from
OL,8,Flonger hikes to short pleasure walks,
OL,9,Fwith one designed to be wheel-friendly
OL,10,Ffor wheelchair users.
OL,12,FOthers offer something extra, with
OL,13,FLynda Stoddart from Take to the Water
OL,14,Fhosting a walk then swim in the River
OL,15,FTweed.
OL,17,F"The walking festival is about the
OL,18,Fexercise, being outdoors and
OL,19,Fmindfulness as well," Lynda said.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
