OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1777381871
OL,3,CBest foot forward: Walking Festival
OL,4,Cgets underway
OL,6,F"Being a present to nature. And
OL,7,Fswimming is very much about that too.
OL,9,F"So we go into nature, we find a water
OL,10,Fwhich is nice, calm, and tranquil. And
OL,11,Fwe have that mindfulness presence when
OL,12,Fwe're going into the water.
OL,14,F"So it's a wonderful opportunity to
OL,15,Ftie in a very short walk with a swim
OL,16,Fas well, and encouraging people to to
OL,17,Fdo both, to get outdoors and
OL,18,Fexperience the water as well."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
